== 澳俄冷战 ==
鉴于俄罗斯对[[马来西亚航空17号班机空难|马来西亚航空17号班机空难]]的反应，以及[[2014年乌克兰亲俄罗斯武装冲突|今年早些时候支持乌克兰的行动]]，澳大利亚和其他[[北约|北约]]国家就是否允许[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]参加会议的问题产生分歧。{{Link-en|澳大利亚外交部长|Minister for Foreign Affairs (Australia)}}[[朱莉·毕晓普|朱莉·毕晓普]]拉拢其他G20国家，意图禁止普京参与会议，指出排除了普京也能达成共识<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-09-21/g20-nations-divided-over-putin-ban-in-brisbane/5758536 |title=G20 nations split on Russian leader Vladimir Putin's visit to Brisbane, Julie Bishop says |author=Kristy Sexton-McGrath |accessdate=2014-10-12 |date=2014-09-21 |publisher=[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳大利亚广播公司]] |archive-date=2014-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011004841/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-09-21/g20-nations-divided-over-putin-ban-in-brisbane/5758536 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年7月的一项民意调查显示，49%的澳大利亚人不同意普京参与会议<ref>{{cite web|url=http://essentialvision.com.au/putin-at-g20|title=Putin at G20|publisher=|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016193006/http://essentialvision.com.au/putin-at-g20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月，[[托尼·阿博特|阿博特]]证实普京将出席会议，并指出“20国集团是透过协商达成一致的国际盛会，轮不到澳大利亚和个别20集团成员作主<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-10-12/putin-confirmed-to-attend-g20-in-brisbane/5807302 |title=Vladimir Putin confirmed to attend G20 in Brisbane, Joe Hockey expects 'full and frank dialogue' at meeting |author= |accessdate=2014-10-12 |date=2014-10-12 |publisher=[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳大利亚广播公司]] |archive-date=2014-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012064226/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-10-12/putin-confirmed-to-attend-g20-in-brisbane/5807302 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

2014年11月，俄罗斯派出舰队进入澳大利亚海岸对开的国际水域，为普京保驾护航。舰队包括[[瓦朗格号|瓦朗格号]]、[[薩波什尼科夫元帥號驅逐艦|薩波什尼科夫元帥號驅逐艦]]、一辆打捞救援船和一艘补给舰。对此，澳大利亚派遣斯图尔特号和帕拉马塔号，并用P-3猎户座侦察机监察俄罗斯的举动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theage.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/russia-sends-warships-towards-australia-before-g20-meeting-20141112-11lc4z.html|title=Russia sends warships towards Australia before G20 meeting|author=David Wroe|work=The Age|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2014-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114162101/http://www.theage.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/russia-sends-warships-towards-australia-before-g20-meeting-20141112-11lc4z.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nguoi-viet.com/absolutenm2/templates/viewarticlesNVO.aspx?articleid=198142&zoneid=5#.VGaXavldXl4 Russian warships near Australia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nguoi-viet.com/absolutenm2/templates/viewarticlesNVO.aspx?articleid=198142&zoneid=5#.VGaXavldXl4 |date=20141129032016 }}. {{vi}}. Retrieved 2014-11-14.</ref>。尽管俄罗斯派遣军舰陪同总统出席国际峰会早有先例，但东道国不知道舰队的规模，这才导致前所未有的这一幕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/25496667/russian-warships-bearing-down-on-australia/|title=Russian warships bearing down on Australia|publisher=|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019074156/http://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/25496667/russian-warships-bearing-down-on-australia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

普京在峰会正式开幕前不久提前离开。加拿大总理[[史蒂芬·哈珀|史蒂芬·哈珀]]对普京说：“我虽然会跟你握手，但我还得告诫您不要插手乌克兰。”这一幕发生在普京接近哈珀和其他G-20领导人时，主动向哈珀伸手。而普京的回应是：“那是不可能的，我们又不在那<ref name=cbcn20141115>{{cite news |title=Stephen Harper at G20 tells Vladimir Putin to 'get out of Ukraine' : Annual summit dominated by Western anger towards Putin |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/stephen-harper-at-g20-tells-vladimir-putin-to-get-out-of-ukraine-1.2836382 |accessdate=2014-11-16 |work=CBC News |publisher=cbc.ca |date=2014-11-15 |archive-date=2014-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115231603/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/stephen-harper-at-g20-tells-vladimir-putin-to-get-out-of-ukraine-1.2836382 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

